decks.notes: This deck revolves around utilizing instant and sorcery spells to control the game and disrupt the opponent's strategy while setting up a combo finish with Brain Freeze or high tide into a large Brainstorm. The commander, Lier, Disciple of the Drowned, allows for spells to be cast from the graveyard, providing additional value and flexibility. The deck includes a high number of cantrips, counterspells, and spell tutors to ensure consistency in finding the key pieces needed to win the game. By efficiently managing resources and disrupting the opponent's plays, this aggro-control deck aims to outpace and outmaneuver the opponent to secure a victory in the 1 vs 1 format of Duel Commander.

The deck is centered around using aggressive strategies with Ketramose, the New Dawn as the commander to quickly overpower opponents. It includes a mix of powerful creatures like Elesh Norn, Mother of Machines and Sheoldred, the Apocalypse, along with disruptive spells like Thoughtseize and Inquisition of Kozilek to keep opponents on their toes. The deck also utilizes removal spells such as Swords to Plowshares and Fatal Push to deal with threats efficiently. With a mana base that includes various fetch lands and dual lands, the deck aims to establish a strong board presence early on and maintain pressure throughout the game to secure a victory.
